Company Description: Operational Since 1948, Mcdonald's Has Been One Of The Leading Global Foodservice Retailers IN The World. Its Menu Consists Of Various Items, Including Burgers, Sandwiches, Chicken, Breakfast, Salads, Snacks And Sides, Beverages, Desserts And Shakes. The Firm Operates More Than 32,000 Local Restaurants Serving Over 60 Million People IN 117 Countries Each Day. For Over 20 Years, Mcdonald's Has Maintained Its Partnership With Environmental Defense Fund, A Nonprofit Organization Specializing IN Creating Transformational Solutions For Environmental Problems.

Established IN 1948, Mcdonald's Is A Fast-Food Company. Located IN East Hanover, N.J., It Is A Global Food Service Retailer Operating One Of The Largest Chains Of Franchised Outlets. The Restaurant's Menu Consists Of Various Items, Including Burgers, Sandwiches, Salads, Snacks And Sides, Beverages, Desserts And Shakes. It Also Offers Some Of Its Flagship Products, Including Big Mac Sandwich, Quarter Pounder, Chicken Mcnuggets, Egg Mcmuffin And Mcgourmet Dinners. Mcdonald's Provides Both, A Fruit And Vegetable Option For Its Trademark Happy Meals, Such As Fruit Bags, Corn Cups And Apple Dippers. The Company Also Offers Entertainment Options, Such As Free WI-Fi, Arch Cards/Play Places And Party Services.
